  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators evaluate the usefulness of lung ultrasonography in the perioperative period
      for postoperative outcomes in children undergoing fast track cardiac surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Some appropriate intervention such as recruitment maneuver, chest tube insertion, or
      diuretics will be applied depending on lung ultrasound findings.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
